channel.title: Pi compiler error (event manager)
channel.description:
Just added a event manager that i was told works for pi, got these 9 errors:
[code]source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:28: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager private List<EventContainer> events; ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:33: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager private Queue<EventContainer> newEvents; ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:99: cannot find symbol symbol : class Event location: class server.event.EventManager public void addEvent(Event event, int tick) { ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:46: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager events = new ArrayList<EventContainer>(); ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:47: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager newEvents = new ArrayDeque<EventContainer>(); ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:76: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager EventContainer event; ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:81: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager for (Iterator<EventContainer> it = events.iterator(); it.hasNext();) { ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:82: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager EventContainer container = it.next(); ^ source\server\model\players\EventManager.java:101: cannot find symbol symbol : class EventContainer location: class server.event.EventManager newEvents.add(new EventContainer(event, tick)); ^ Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 9 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Help greatly appreciated! Thanks.
